Package by.bsuir.task2.entity.criteria

Class Criteria

java.lang.Object
by.bsuir.task2.entity.criteria.Criteria
public class Criteria extends Object
The Criteria class represents search criteria on a single field of an appliance. It consists of the criteria itself (field), search type (either EQUALS, LESS THAN or GREATER THAN) and the value to compare with
